Title: Sequential Analyses
Description: The documents provided here should help researchers to perform sequential analyses. It provides an introduction to sequential analyses, two step-by-step guides (using either R or WinDL software) and a spreadsheet that can be used to perform some additional calculations.
Contributors: Daniel Lakens
Tags: sequential analyses, power, statistics, adaptive designs

Sequential Analyses
The documents provided here should help researchers to perform sequential analyses. It provides an introduction to sequential analyses, two step-by-step guides (using either R or WinDL software) and a spreadsheet that can be used to perform some additional calculations.
